> MDFJ:
moon install [package]       → Installs a package or game (.vge)
moon update on [package]     → Turns on automatic updates for the package
moon update off [package]    → Turns off automatic updates for the package
actualict moon [package]     → Manually updates the package
moon open [package] → open app for vía web. 
pc settings                 → Opens the settings menu
# Inside the menu:
1. System                   → General system settings
2. Application              → Install or manage apps and packages
3. Battery                  → RAM and energy optimization
4. Hardware                 → View CPU, RAM, disks
5. Network                  → Configure servers and connections
6. Exit                     → Exit the menu
apt -v                      → Shows system version
carl -ver                   → Shows terminal version
apt shell update install    → Updates the terminal in 1 minute
# Used inside pc settings → Application
pc install [language]        → Installs languages like Python, Node.js, Oracle
pc principal install main.py → Installs main files for each language
hardware pc ram             → Shows RAM amount
hardware pc cpu             → Shows number of CPU cores
